#Suppose the cover price of a book
#is dollar 24.95, but bookstores get a
#40 cent discount. Shipping
#costs $3 for the first copy and 75
#cents for each additional copy. What
#is the total wholesale cost for 60
#copies
price= 24.95
discount= 0.4
fc_ship=3
ad_ship=0.75
n=60
total_book=n*(price-discount)
print(total_book)
total_ship=(n-1)*ad_ship+fc_ship
print(total_ship)
total=total_book+total_ship
print(total)
